.TH "emac_update_hw_stats" 9 "emac_update_hw_stats" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
emac_update_hw_stats \- read the EMAC stat registers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" emac_update_hw_stats
.BI "(struct emac_adapter *adpt "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "adpt" 12
pointer to adapter struct
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Reads the stats registers and write the values to adpt->stats.

adpt->stats.lock must be held while calling this function,
and while reading from adpt->stats.
